title.narrative: Routine Immunisation: Procurement of Goods for DFID MNCH

description.narrative: This activity (Routine Immunisation: Procurement of Goods for DFID MNCH) is a component of Routine Immunisation reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of goods' and a budget of £4,640,951. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Reproductive health care. , with the following implementing partners: Crown Agents Limited. The start date is 01-04-2011 and the end date is 31-07-2014.
